Silvercorp Says KPMG to Issue Report on Fraud Allegations ’Soon’

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-09-26T03:54:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/silvercorp-says-kpmg-to-issue-report-on-fraud-allegations-soon-.html
Silvercorp Metals Inc. (SVM) , a Canadian
miner accused of fraud in two anonymous reports, said it has
hired KPMG Forensics Inc. to check the company’s cash flows and
production volumes to counter allegations of fraud, and it will
release its results “soon,” Company Chief Executive Feng Rui
said in an interview in Beijing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 swong139@bloomberg.net  